maintext:
Freddy Cano
School: Ben Lomond
Grade level: Junior
Position: Forward
Nickname: Freddy
Favorite food: Pizza
Favorite TV show: Friends
Favorite movie: “The Hunger Games: Catching Fire”
Favorite band/singer: Bryson Tiller
Favorite class/subject: English
Favorite athlete: Lionel Messi
Favorite hobby: Playing soccer
Favorite board game/card game: Uno
Favorite website/app/video game: Fortnite
What I’d like to win a lifetime supply of (other than money): Hot Cheetos
Most exciting sports moment you’ve ever been a part of: Scored a game-winner in a regional club soccer playoff game two summers ago.
Best advice ever received: Everything is about mental strength.
Plans after high school: Study sports psychology, try to play professional soccer.
Performance review: Scored two goals, including the game-winner, in a 3-2 win over Ogden on March 30. Earlier that week in a 4-1 win over Tooele, Cano scored two goals as well.
